## Quality bar — self-check before delivering

- [ ] The decision is one unambiguous sentence in the active voice.
- [ ] DRI and approver are real, people-search-resolved names — not roles.
- [ ] At least two options are recorded with the reason the chosen one won.
- [ ] The KPI the decision moves is named, with its value at decision time.
- [ ] Compliance/control implication is recorded, even if "none."
- [ ] Every follow-up has an owner and a due date; a review date is set.
- [ ] The source thread or meeting is linked; any superseded decision is cross-linked.
- [ ] No Confidential or labeled content is pasted into the record — summarized and linked instead.

If any check fails, fix it before saving to the log.
